text:
Yesterday, TGH's Vanessa Arroyo became the first nurse in FL to receive the #COVID19 #vaccine:

"This morning my six year old daughter came up to me and said 'Mommy, I'm so proud of you that you got that shot.' My husband had watched it on the news with my two young kids." (1/4) https://t.co/JyFgRqwQKz
